text: Cribbin is a surname, and may refer to: * J. J. Cribbin, Irish priest and Gaelic footballer who played for Ballyhaunis and Mayo * Larry Cribbin, Irish Gaelic footballer who played for Clane and Kildare * Tom Cribbin, Irish Gaelic footballer who played for Clane and managed Clane, Laois, Offaly and Westmeath ==See also== * Bernard Cribbins, English actor Category:Surnames
title: Cribbin
